<h2>About HealthTrack</h2>

<p>HealthTrack helps you monitor and track your health and fitness activities in one convenient place.</p>

<h3>Core Technologies</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Server:</strong> Node.js with the Express framework.</li>
    <li><strong>Templating:</strong> EJS (Embedded JavaScript) for dynamic view generation.</li>
    <li><strong>Database:</strong> MySQL for persistent data storage.</li>
    <li><strong>Security:</strong> bcrypt for password hashing and express-session for user authorization.</li>
    <li><strong>Input Security:</strong> express-validator for form data validation and express-sanitizer for input sanitization.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Features</h3>
<ul>
    <li>User registration and secure login</li>
    <li>Add and track health/fitness activities</li>
    <li>View your personal activity history</li>
    <li>Search all activities by keyword</li>
</ul>